{
  "texts": [
    "The databases we use to collect papers are those of the search engines Scopus and Web of Science.",
    "To limit the scope of research to the application of RL approaches for environmental sustainability, we define the following search strings:",
    "• \"reinforcement learning AND sustainable AND environment\";",
    "• \"reinforcement learning AND environmental AND sustainability\";",
    "• \"reinforcement learning AND environment AND sustainability\";"
  ]
}